1. The objective is to establish how to administer Power BI as a tool. This includes, among other things:

User Access Management – How to grant and manage access for users to the platform.

Workspace Organization – How to structure and organize workspaces in a logical and efficient manner.

User Access Levels – What level of access users have within their respective workspaces (e.g., Admin, Member, Contributor, Viewer).


2. The objective is to evaluate the different ways to connect Power BI with Datasphere


